snippet.textDisplay:
I have a friend that ive known since maybe 2014 or so right. my friends and i called him goose due to his username Goosechaser. And for the longest time we didnt even know his actual name. But learning that didnt take as long as seeing his face. We are like his closest friends and we didnt see his face until like 2018-2019. He made a discord server named caFe leveaR which was an anagram for Face Reveal (took me way too long to figure it out). and the one date associated with it was April 1st. Well we always joked about him being a literal goose or wearing a goose mask all the time.


Well when April 1st came around we were all added to a call. Our friend group of about 8 people or so in a video call. Goose turns on his web cam and we are treated to the site of a guy wearing a duck mask with a rasta hat on. Everyone is fucking hyper. He takes off the hat and pulls off the mask to reveal a FUCKING GOOSE MASK UNDERNEATH! Funniest shit right. Finally he takes off the mask and we get to see the friend we've known for like half a decade. Best shit ever.



That summer his family was going on a road trip to yellowstone and unbeknownst to me they were coming up from Florida and through my great state of Michigan. So im sitting down in my basement playing games as usual when i hear someone almost fall down my fucking stairs. I look to the door and around the corner comes the fucker with his god damn GOOSE MASK AND RASTA HAT! Funniest shit ever man. I love my friends.
